LOC TRACKING MECHANISM
The AI agent MUST track LOC count accurately to determine WT create milestones. 
HT TRACK LOC
Use git diff --stat to measure code changes: 
CODE bash 278CHARS
LOC CALCULATION
Extract the total LOC count from the summary line: 
PATTERN `X files changed, Y insertions(+), Z deletions(-)`
ACCUMULATION ACROSS CHUNKS
CRITICAL: Track cumulative LOC across multiple implementation chunks: 
CODE python 551CHARS
STOP THRESHOLD
Stop when: cumulative_loc = 800 AND tests are not all passing Continue if: cumulative_loc < 800 OR all tests pass (nearing completion) Exception: If very close to completion (750 LOC and 90% tests pass), continue to finish 
