CRITICAL: Local-Only Checkpoint Files 
Milestone documents in .tmp/milestones/ are LOCAL CHECKPOINT FILES ONLY: 
DO NOT stage these files: git add .tmp/milestones/ is FORBIDDEN DO NOT force-add these files: git add -f .tmp/milestones/* is FORBIDDEN DO NOT commit these files under any circumstances These files are automatically excluded by .gitignore when using git add . 
Why .tmp/milestones/ files must remain local: 
TA working notes for resuming implementation between sessions They contain partial progress states not suitable for repository history .gitignore already excludes them to prevent accidental staging Only completed implementation code/tests/docs should be committed 
